This product is an INDEPENDENT, clean-room plugin. It is not affiliated with,
endorsed by, or derived from the source code of aaPanel / 宝塔 (Dongguan Baita
Network Technology Co., Ltd.). It interoperates with the panel solely through
the panel's public, documented third-party plugin API. It contains no aaPanel
source code, UI layout, icons, or text.

At runtime the plugin downloads and manages the following third-party software,
which it does NOT bundle or redistribute:

  * Apache Tomcat            — Apache License 2.0   (https://tomcat.apache.org)
  * Eclipse Temurin / OpenJDK — GPLv2 with Classpath Exception (https://adoptium.net)
  * PostgreSQL JDBC Driver    — BSD-2-Clause        (https://jdbc.postgresql.org)

Downloads are integrity-verified (SHA-512, and OpenPGP where signatures are
published) before use.
